long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1270169 debug log
Description of problem: tesseract cannot be selected for OCR, only GOCR can be used.
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable): gscan2pdf.noarch 1.7.3-1.fc26 tesseract.x86_64 3.05.00-1.fc26 tesseract-langpack-deu.noarch 3.05.00-1.fc26
How reproducible: always
Steps to Reproduce: 1. Start gscan2pdf 2. Enable "OCR scanned pages" 3. Try to select tesseract instead of GOCR
Actual results: Only GOCR can be selected.
Expected results: Both options (GOCR and tesseract) can be selected.
Additional info: This issue does not occur in F25.
Both F26 and F25 has the same gscan2pdf. But tesseract was upgraded from 3.04.01-2.fc25 to 3.05.00-1.fc26.
